# ONNX Runtime Web WASM assets (issue #27). Copied from the installed
# onnxruntime-web package by `scripts/copy-ort-wasm.mjs` (run automatically by
# the frontend build), not committed to git. Served same-origin under
# /models/ort/ so nothing is fetched from a CDN at runtime (CLAUDE.md; §1.3/§8).
*.wasm
*.mjs
!.gitignore
!README.md
